== Challenges ==

A feature which lets you complete challenges<ref>`Complete!` `When the player completes all their challenges` [https://crowdin.com/editor/vrchat-application/19#130850 Crowdin]</ref><ref>`All Challenges Completed!` `When the player completes all their assigned challenges` [https://crowdin.com/editor/vrchat-application/19#130854 Crowdin]</ref>. First discovery on December 13, 2024. Last new discovery on December 16, 2024. This feature is not yet accessible to all users, and seems to only be available for some VRChat accounts.

Challenges:
* Make X Friends<ref>`Make {0} Friends`, `A challenge for players to make {0} number of friends.` - [https://crowdin.com/editor/vrchat-application/19#130852 Crowdin]</ref>
* Visit X Friends<ref>`Visit {0} Worlds`, `Challenge description: When a player visit X number of worlds.` - [https://crowdin.com/editor/vrchat-application/19#130860 Crowdin]</ref>
* Visit X Worlds<ref name="crowdin130860">`Visit {0} Worlds`, `Challenge description: When a player visit X number of worlds.` - [https://crowdin.com/editor/vrchat-application/19#130860 Crowdin]</ref> (Reward [[Special:MyLanguage/Badges|badge]]: World Explorer<ref name="WorldExplorer />)
* Try VRChat on Another Platform<ref>`Try VRChat on Another Platform`, `Challenge description: When a player plays VRC on another platform` - [https://crowdin.com/editor/vrchat-application/19#130856 Crowdin]</ref>
* Log in X Days in a Row<ref>`Log in {0} Days in a Row`, `Challenge description: When a player logs in X number of days in a row.` - [https://crowdin.com/editor/vrchat-application/19#130858 Crowdin]</ref>

